item.title: Online errors
item.dc:creator: @DannyIsSoPro DannyIsSoPro
item.description:
@DannyIsSoPro wrote:

Josephx:

My server was online for a whilebut then my internet went off for a second and i cant get serve rback online since… I have firewall disabled, I portForwarded, i changed my classpath and path but its still not online.

LOLWUT. My best guess is that your router/modem reset and … well your ports you forwarded aren’t there anymore. Also, check if your NO-IP hasn’t been disabled due to inactivity, since now they disable unpaid hosts every 30 days if they’re not updated or checked…
